Class ConfigPathNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.codekutter.zconfig.common.model.nodes.AbstractConfigNode
      • com.codekutter.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigElementNode
        • com.codekutter.zconfig.common.model.nodes.ConfigPathNode

  • public class ConfigPathNode
extends ConfigElementNode
    Class represents a configuration path node.

    Configuration path(s) can be represented using a (.) or (/) notation while referencing.
